ed on user's question."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best for"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Structured data (tables, records)\n- Query-based retrieval patterns\n- Enterprise databases with existing schemas"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"RAG System Architecture with Vector Search"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Complete Flow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Question\n    ↓\nDownstream Application (RAG pipeline)\n    ↓\nKnowledge Base (Vector Database)\n    ↓\nRetrieval: Find most relevant vector embeddings\n    ↓\nTop-k chunks returned\n    ↓\nAugmented Prompt (chunks + question)\n    ↓\nLLM (Generator)\n    ↓\nGrounded Response"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key insight"},{"type":"text","text":": The vector database is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"retrieval engine"},{"type":"text","text":" — when user asks a question, it finds most relevant document chunks and passes them to LLM as context."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Search Methods"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Method"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Uses"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type